| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0524 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomexx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ac01c844-55ea-54b7-88e3-67620e1dd6f5"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
